This step hunts for file activity related to bonus payout/bonus matrix artifacts on **sys1-dept** and extracts remote session device metadata to determine whether a specialized departmental remote session was involved in accessing sensitive payout files.

‚úÖ Finding  
Activity on **sys1-dept** shows the following remote session department interacting with bonus payout/bonus matrix‚Äìrelated files:  
