### üîé What to Hunt
File events related to bonus payout artifacts and extract the remote session device metadata.  
Hint: Utilize previous findings.

### ‚ùó Why it matters
Use of a planning/HR remote session to access payout artifacts suggests the attacker is intentionally focusing on high-value business data and may be leveraging privileged departmental access to progress the intrusion.

### üîç KQL Query Used
```kql
DeviceFileEvents
| where TimeGenerated >= datetime(2025-12-01)
| where DeviceName == "sys1-dept"
